\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}, {\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996271072, \"rank\": 3.726898402785281e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999947422536001, \"rank\": 5.256232337991006e-06, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was also a one point difference between the Indian pair and Serbia in second place.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9915672066457752, \"rank\": 0.008460517825479696, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999527017291, \"rank\": 4.727754419250281e-08, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bhaker was solid in her first two series with scores of 98, but a 95 in the third series saw the team slip into the bronze medal match spots.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh, who had failed to qualify for the individual final, shot 97 in the second and third series.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\