": 2532, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9915672066457752, \"rank\": 0.008460517825479696, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was yet another fourth-place finish for an Indian in the men's 10m air rifle final after Abhinav Bindra finished outside the podium spots back in Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2717, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9915672066457752, \"rank\": 0.008460517825479696, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abhinav Bindra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\"}, {\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998917701, \"rank\": 1.0811460547309364e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old shooter began the final in top form, consistently shooting near the centre of the target to end the first series in third place with a score of 105.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two shots later, Babuta was in second place and just 0.1 points behind the eventual gold medallist and world record holder Sheng Lihao of China.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3134, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8884360314448422, \"rank\": 0.12554029655490734, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued to remain in second place for one more series, but then began to slip from the fifth series onwards.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With Victor Lindgren of Sweden and Miran Maricic of Croatia at his heels, Babuta was unable to open up a gap and ended with a 9.5 to ultimately finish fourth with a score of 208.4.\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3262, \"end\": 3268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"score\": 0.9759579648612565, \"rank\": 0.012939241021742855, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\"}, {\"begin\": 3281, \"end\": 3287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8978293476305508, \"rank\": 0.11096829436186775, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miran_Pastourma\", \"score\": 0.9999999998121893, \"rank\": 1.8610221373394514e-10, \"text\": \"Miran\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miran_Pastourma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miran_Pastourma\"}, {\"begin\": 3309, \"end\": 3316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9761351642095172, \"rank\": 0.024448220629631777, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's 10m air rifle final, Jindal found herself in fourth place after the first five shots, but ended up slipping to seventh place after 10 shots with a score of 104.\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2022 Asian Games medallist saved herself with a shot of 10.5 to move into sixth and eliminate Norway's Hegg Jeanette Duestad.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3714, \"end\": 3720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.94819072206402, \"rank\": 0.05457869980873558, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3728, \"end\": 3736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.736837423364041e-19, \"text\": \"Jeanette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the next elimination, the Indian was tied with France's Oceanne Muller with a score of 145.3 and went to a shoot-off where the local favourite shot 10.8 to Jindal's 10.5 which saw the Indian be eliminated from the final.\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3779, \"end\": 3785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.99156720664